    <h3>Purpose and Function</h3>
    GGarbage Collector is an application for reporting objects that can be useful and have been filed on the sidewalks.<br/><br/>
    Here are our tips for using the app:<br/>
    To deposit an object please select the tab "Add", then take a picture of the object to deposit. The application locate you with the GPS, and determinate the object\'s address. It only remains for you to validate your ad.<br/><br/>
    To find an object select the tabs "offers" or "Card". The tab "Offers" allows you to sort the objects surrounding by category and/or timing of deposits or distance. The "Maps" tab allows you to view objects through Google Maps, you can also perform a sort on categories.<br/>

    <h3>About us</h3>
    Valha Tech is a start-up turning to the mobile development.<br/>

    <h3>Ethics</h3>
    We use the state of your Internet connection in order to ensure the proper functioning of the application Garbage Collector.<br/><br/>
